# textdomain: mcl_panes
Glass panes are thin layers of glass which neatly connect to their neighbors as you build them.=유리판은 얇은 유리 층으로, 배치하면 이웃한 유리판과 매끄럽게 연결됩니다.
Stained glass panes are thin layers of stained glass which neatly connect to their neighbors as you build them. They come in many different colors.=염색 유리판은 얇은 염색 유리 층으로 배치하면 이웃하는 유리판과 매끄럽게 연결됩니다. 다양한 색상이 있습니다.
Stained Glass Pane=염색 유리판
Iron Bars=철 창살
Iron bars neatly connect to their neighbors as you build them.=
